1. On je započeo *igru* (He started the game).
2. Oni su se igrali *igre* (They were playing games).
3. Učenici u školi vole da igraju *igru* (The students in school like to play the game).
4. Ona je uživala u *igranju* (She enjoyed playing).
5. Mi smo se igrali *igrica* (We were playing games).
6. Oni su igrali *igru* sinoć (They were playing the game last night).
7. On je učio pravila *igre* (He was learning the rules of the game).
8. Mi smo zabavno *igrali* (We were having fun playing).